snippet.title: Lake Ridden Alpha Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam Store Page. Wishlist and follow now!http://store.steampowered.com/app/696530/Lake_Ridden/

Early alpha trailer showing upcoming mystery game Lake Ridden by Midnight Hub. Release for PC spring 2018. On a camping trip during the last days of autumn, your sister disappears in the middle of the night. Read more: http://www.midnighthub.com/

Drop us an email to play the full demo at GDC & Game Connection 2017: contact@midnighthub.com!

Lake Ridden is a puzzle mystery where you’ll uncover dark secrets of the past trying to bring home your sister. It will be released for PC in 2018.

http://www.midnighthub.com/
https://www.facebook.com/midnighthub/
https://www.twitter.com/midnighthub

Music: Ghost Note Music http://www.patrikjarlestam.se/index2.htm
Voice Actress: Klister Media http://www.klister.media/
